article_id:1852,category_name:News,title_name:Chapter 17: The City of Grams Added to the Main Campaign, and More Dragons Can Be Unbound Using Draconic Essences!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2bc983490255730586e888f0b84f1db2.png,message:<div>Chapter 17: The City of Grams was added to the main campaign at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1608271200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2bc983490255730586e888f0b84f1db2.png"></div><div><br></div><div>After entering North Grastaea, the prince and his friends make for the Holy City of Grams in order to search for a man by the name of Gatov. But they quickly find themselves hunted by forces from the Ilian Church, while Ranzal encounters Volk once more. Will they have the strength to overcome the many trials ahead?</div><div><br></div><div>We hope you&#39;re looking forward seeing what&#39;s in store for the prince and his friends!</div><div><br></div><div>Also, as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1608271200"></span>, more dragons can be unbound using draconic essences. Draconic essences have been added for the following dragons:</div><div>・Arctos</div><div>・Kamuy</div><div>・Freyja</div><div>・Takemikazuchi</div><div>・Epimetheus</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Chapter 17: The City of Grams will unlock when you clear Chapter 16 / 4-6 &quot;Setting Off.&quot;</div><div>2. You can use the draconic essence icon displayed on the area map for each chapter in the main campaign to check the dragon whose draconic essence you can obtain, how many draconic essences you currently have, how many more you can obtain, and the quests from which you can obtain draconic essences.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1608271200,update_time1608023539